set_amount

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_amount -  This method sets the amount the credit note is for.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_amount(int amount)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^amount%^RESET%^ - the amount the note is for

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/misc/bank_credit_note.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the amount the credit note is for.  +ve means that
we are transporting money to the master bank, -ve means we are taking
money out of the master bank.
.EP

